# Budget-Bandhu — Complete Repository Analysis

> **Date:** 2026-03-29 | **Version:** v4.2 Unified API | **Focus:** Full repo map for merging prep

---

## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend ["budget-bandhu-frontend (Next.js 16.1)"]
        FE_Pages["Pages (13 routes)"]
        FE_Comps["Components (~60)"]
        FE_Wallet["MetaMask Integration"]
    end

    subgraph Backend ["budget-bandhu-rag (FastAPI v4.2)"]
        API["14 Routers"]
        Agents["Agent Controller + Phi3 RAG"]
        DB["MongoDB (motor async)"]
        Services["IPFS + Minting Services"]
    end

    subgraph ML ["budget-bandhu-models (PyTorch/sklearn)"]
        Forecaster["BiLSTM Forecaster"]
        Categorizer["SentenceTransformer Categorizer"]
        Anomaly["IsolationForest Anomaly"]
        QLearning["Q-Learning Policy"]
    end

    subgraph Web3 ["budget-bandhu-web3 (Hardhat/Solidity)"]
        SBT["GoalBadgeSBT (ERC-721)"]
        Escrow["GroupEscrow"]
    end

    FE_Pages --> API
    FE_Wallet --> SBT & Escrow
    API --> DB
    API --> Services
    Services --> SBT
    API --> ML
```

