### 3. `budget-bandhu-models/` — ML Microservice

| Model | File | Architecture | Purpose |
|-------|------|-------------|---------|
| **Forecaster** | [forecaster.py](file:///Users/aditya4/Desktop/Budget-Bandhu/budget-bandhu-models/intelligence/forecaster.py) | BiLSTM (PyTorch), 2-layer bidirectional, 128 hidden → 7-day forecast × 6 categories | Spending forecast per category |
| **Categorizer** | [categorizer.py](file:///Users/aditya4/Desktop/Budget-Bandhu/budget-bandhu-models/intelligence/categorizer.py) | all-MiniLM-L6-v2 → LogisticRegression → 10 Indian UPI categories | Auto-categorization of transactions |
| **Anomaly Detector** | [anomaly_detector.py](file:///Users/aditya4/Desktop/Budget-Bandhu/budget-bandhu-models/intelligence/anomaly_detector.py) | IsolationForest + 5 rule-based checks (SPIKE, DUPLICATE, OFF_HOURS, NEW_MERCHANT, VELOCITY) | Fraud/anomaly detection |
| **Policy Learner** | [intelligence/policy_learner.py](file:///Users/aditya4/Desktop/Budget-Bandhu/budget-bandhu-models/intelligence/policy_learner.py) | Q-Learning | Budget recommendations |
| **ML Pipeline** | [intelligence/ml_pipeline.py](file:///Users/aditya4/Desktop/Budget-Bandhu/budget-bandhu-models/intelligence/ml_pipeline.py) | Orchestrates all models | Unified inference pipeline |

**Pre-trained model artifacts** in [models/](file:///Users/aditya4/Desktop/Budget-Bandhu/budget-bandhu-models/intelligence/forecaster.py#86-109):
- `isolation_forest/` — model.joblib, scaler.joblib, category_stats.json
- `lstm_forecaster/` — scaler.joblib, categories.json (no model.pt = moving average fallback)
- `phi3_categorizer/` — classifier.joblib, label_encoder.joblib
- `q_learning/` — state_encoder.joblib, training_metadata.json

