## 🔗 Data Flow Map

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/MetaMask
    participant FE as Frontend (Next.js)
    participant BE as Backend (FastAPI)
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant ML as ML Models
    participant IPFS as Pinata IPFS
    participant BC as Polygon Amoy

    Note over U,BC: Personal CSV Goal Flow
    U->>FE: Create goal (target ₹20k, salary ₹40k)
    FE->>BE: POST /goals
    BE->>DB: Insert goal doc
    U->>FE: Upload CSV
    FE->>BE: POST /goals/{id}/progress
    BE->>BE: Parse CSV → savings = salary - spend
    BE->>DB: Update goal.current
    BE-->>FE: {is_complete: true}
    U->>FE: Click "Mint Badge"
    FE->>BE: POST /goals/{id}/complete
    BE->>BE: PIL generates badge image
    BE->>IPFS: Upload image → imageCID
    BE->>IPFS: Upload metadata → metaCID
    BE->>BC: mintBadge(wallet, tokenURI)
    BC-->>BE: tx_hash
    BE->>DB: Store badge_tx_hash, token_uri
    BE-->>FE: Success + badge data
    FE->>U: Badge popup (image, download, Polygonscan)

    Note over U,BC: Personal Crypto Goal Flow
    U->>FE: Click "Sync Wallet"
    FE->>U: MetaMask → switch to Amoy
    FE->>BC: eth_getBalance
    BC-->>FE: Balance in wei
    FE->>BE: PUT /goals/{id}/progress/manual {amount, mode: "set"}
    BE->>DB: Update goal.current
```

